main event: An unidentified aircraft was reported by a flight crew of Quants 586 en route from Nandi to Honolulu.
interesting points: The flight crew saw lights from another aircraft moving east at about 35,000 feet., When the Quants turned their landing lights on, the other aircraft extinguished all their lights., No other air traffic was reported in the area during the incident., The sighting was made during clear weather conditions., The report was filed as a record with Project Blue Book.
